The art of etching and aqua tinting

London: Printed for J. Barker, 1797. Fullstendig tittel: "The art of etching and aqua tinting : strictly laid down by the most approved masters; sufficiently enabling amateurs in drawing to transmit their works to posterity; or, As amusements among their circle of friends. To which is added, The most useful liquid colours, well adapted for staining and colouring the above, &c." Illustrasjoner i etsning og akvatint. Fem sider med håndskrevne notater og en utbrettsannonse.
